desc: Boosts max HP and Atk by 30%, Def by 15%, boosts BC drop rate & boosts Def against Dark elemental damage

dictionary.lore: A special sword forged from Mithril by royal Elysian blacksmiths. It was given to Xenon as a token of honor from the Elysian King for dedicating his life as a protector of the realm.

name: Xentar
